s" content="bbq rub" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="More effort" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Barbecue" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Summer" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Indulgent" /></div></div><div class="recipe-header__description" itemprop="description"><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden method__content"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Once you&#39;ve tried smoking and slow cooking your chicken, you&#39;ll be totally converted. The dry brine seasons the meat to the bone and keeps it succulent during cooking</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="recipe-header__bottom"><div class="recipe-header__share service-links__container"><div class="service-links"><div class="service-label">Share:</div><ul class="service-links-primary"><li class="service-links-facebook first"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/texas-bbq-medley&amp;t=Texas%20BBQ%20medley" title="Share on Facebook" class="service-links-facebook service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Facebook"><i class="font-icon font-icon-facebook-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Facebook</span></a></li><li class="service-links-pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/bookmarklet?media=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/recipe/recipe-image/2016/07/texas-bbq-medley-.jpg&amp;url=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/texas-bbq-medley&amp;title=Texas%20BBQ%20medley&amp;is_video=false&amp;description=" title="Pin it on Pinterest" class="service-links-pinterest service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Pinterest"><i class="font-icon font-icon-pinterest-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Pinterest</span></a></li><li class="service-links-twitter"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/texas-bbq-medley&amp;text=Texas%20BBQ%20medley" title="Share this on Twitter" class="ser